    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "When a reorg event occurs the scheduled duties map was cleared, however the duties objects weren't cancelled. So any events that were already pending but waiting for the duties scheduling to load would still be processed once the request for duties came back. This potentially creates a slashable offence as the recalculated duties would also be scheduled.\n\n#2682 will fix it.",
